nodes.text: A human male prisoner was held captive in the city Calodan on the planet Corvus. He was used as a bargaining chip by Magistrate Morgan Elsbeth to prevent the former Jedi Ahsoka Tano from attacking the city.

Wing debuted in "Chapter 13: The Jedi" from the second season of the television series The Mandalorian, which was written and directed by Dave Filoni and released on Disney+ on November 27, 2020. Credited as "Prisoner," he was portrayed by James Croak.
